      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Experience automotive excellence with this pristine, showroom-condition masterpiece. Meticulously maintained and presenting in absolute top-tier form, this vehicle represents the pinnacle of its class. From the flawless exterior finish to the untouched interior, every detail reflects a standard of care rarely seen on the market. This is a rare opportunity for the discerning driver who demands a vehicle that looks and drives as if it just rolled off the assembly line.",
