    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! If you\u2019re looking for a real gem, you\u2019ve found it. I\u2019ve absolutely loved every mile in this beauty, but it\u2019s time for someone else to enjoy that showroom-fresh feeling. It\u2019s been kept in a climate-controlled garage and babied since day one\u2014honestly, it looks and feels like it just rolled off the assembly line. There might be a tiny, barely-visible speck if you look with a magnifying glass, but to me, she\u2019s absolutely perfect. I\u2019d love to see it go to someone who appreciates a car that\u2019s been truly cherished. Swing by and see for yourself!",
      "price": 44900.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 21
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presenting a clinically maintained E46 M3, featuring a bulletproofed S54 power plant with a comprehensive VANOS overhaul and subframe reinforcement already completed for maximum torsional rigidity. This isn't just a driver; it\u2019s a precision instrument. The throttle response is razor-sharp thanks to a calibrated drive-by-wire system and a fresh set of individual throttle bodies. Underneath, you\u2019ll find zero-lash bushings and a thermally optimized cooling stack. The paint depth is consistent across all panels, reflecting a true collector-grade specimen. If you\u2019re looking for a machine that delivers linear power with surgical accuracy, this is the benchmark.",
      "price": 47500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 21
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Flawless. Showroom ready. One owner. Zero issues. Don't wait.",
      "price": 42500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
