    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Step into a world where engineering meets art. This Midnight Sapphire grand tourer is a breathtaking relic of an era when cars were built with soul. The paintwork possesses a depth that seems to swallow the light, shimmering like the deep ocean under a full moon. Inside, you are enveloped in a sanctuary of hand-stitched Connolly leather and mirror-matched walnut veneers that whisper stories of high-society galas and spirited midnight drives. The engine\u2019s purr is a rhythmic symphony, a testament to a life of pampered care and mechanical devotion. This is more than a vehicle; it is a preserved dream, waiting for a driver who appreciates the finer nuances of a truly exceptional machine.",
      "price": 43500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
